        "Description": [
          {
            "text": "Our Portable Camp Lunch Baby Bottle Cooler Bag with Ice Pack is designed for versatility and reliability, perfect for camping, beach trips, or daily use. Crafted from high-quality Oxford fabric, it features thick insulation to maintain temperature—keeping breastmilk cold or warm for up to 8 hours—and a leak-proof, waterproof, wipeable lining for easy cleaning. The durable smooth zipper ensures secure closure, while the convenient side pocket stores essentials like phones and keys. It fits up to 4 baby bottles (9 ounces each) and includes a high-performance ice pack for extended cooling. With a detachable buckle top handle, it easily attaches to strollers, making it ideal for working moms, travelers, and parents on the go. Beyond breastmilk storage, this multifunctional bag doubles as a lunch cooler for fruits, meals, or snacks. Suitable for sustainable lifestyles and anniversary gifting, it combines practicality with durability for all your cooling needs.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
